        <h1>About Notty</h1>
        <p class="lead">Welcome to Notty, the place where laughter and storytelling come together! My name's Kenny, and I'm the creator of this little corner on the internet. Here, I share my quirky and humorous animations that bring to life some of the funniest and most memorable moments from my past.</p>
        <p class="lead">Life is full of unexpected twists and turns, and I like to capture those moments in my videos, creating a delightful blend of animation and storytelling. From hilarious anecdotes to absurd thoughts, you're in for a rollercoaster ride of laughs!</p>
        <p class="lead">As a self-taught animator and storyteller, I put my heart and soul into every video to ensure you have the best possible experience. The goal is simple: to brighten your day and bring a smile to your face!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
