        <h2 class="mt-5">Why Notty?</h2>
        <p>The name "Notty" is a play on the words "not" and "naughty." It represents the mischievous, lighthearted spirit of the content you'll find here. Notty is all about celebrating the little moments that make life entertaining, even if they might be a bit "notty" at times!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row mb-5">
      <div class="col-lg-12">
        <h2 class="mt-5">Join the Fun!</h2>
        <p>I believe that life is better when we share laughter and joy. So, I invite you to join the Notty community! Don't forget to hit that subscribe button and ring the notification bell on my YouTube channel to be the first to watch my latest animations.</p>
        <p>You can also find me on various social media platforms, where I share behind-the-scenes peeks, updates, and connect with my amazing audience.</p>
        <p>Thank you for being a part of Notty's journey. Let's create a world where smiles and laughter reign!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
